abstract: >
  The Medical Record System is a comprehensive mobile application designed for healthcare professionals to manage patient records efficiently. 
  Built with Flutter for cross-platform compatibility, it provides offline capabilities with eventual synchronization to a central server. 
  Key features include patient record creation, file attachment support, secure authentication, advanced search functionality, 
  data export capabilities, and analytics dashboard. The system ensures data availability even in low-connectivity environments while 
  maintaining security and compliance with healthcare regulations.